vative-productive-groups.html" rel=3D"noopener" target=3D"_blank">the small=
 group theory</a>.=E2=80=9D It goes like this:</p>
</blockquote>
<ul style=3D"margin:0px 0px 1em 1em;padding:0px;font-size:14px;line-height:=
1.4em;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,=
Arial,sans-serif"><li style=3D"margin-left:1em;font-size:14px;line-height:1=
.4em;color:rgb(68,68,68);font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,A=
rial,sans-serif"><strong>When working on any kind of problem, task or quest=
ion, embed yourself in a small group of peers with broadly similar concerns=
.</strong></li>
</ul><p style=3D"direction:ltr;font-size:14px;line-height:1.4em;color:rgb(6=
8,68,68);font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;=
margin:0px 0px 1em">And:</p>
<blockquote style=3D"font-family:Times,serif;font-size:1.1em;font-style:ita=
